# SOULDEM CONTRACTS — Environment Variables
# For LOCAL GANACHE: no .env needed at all.
# truffle-config.js already points to 127.0.0.1:7545
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── ONLY NEEDED FOR PUBLIC TESTNET/MAINNET ────
# Leave this file alone if you are using local Ganache.

# MNEMONIC = the 12-word phrase Ganache printed when it started
# (copy it from your terminal — see README for exact steps)
MNEMONIC=""

# Infura project ID — only needed for public networks
INFURA_PROJECT_ID=""
